Pyra and Mythra were only activated for 1 year before going into stasis and they apparently have the mind of a teenager given that Morag, Brighid and Adam who are twenty something treat them like kids. Plus this doujin takes place after the game so it's likely Rex is aged up and Pyra and Mythra should have "aged" too.
